  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Make an Impact by</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain hydraulic, diesel machineries and cable tanks.</li><li>Perform day to day maintenance activities such as oiling & greasing of machineries etc.</li><li>Operate cable hauler during cable transfer operations.</li><li>Lead or supervise other staff or laborer in the riggings or re-riggings for the cable transfer operations.</li><li>Supervise cable coiling during cable transfer operations.</li><li>Any other works as assigned by the Supervisor.</li><li>Occasional shift work required.</li></ul><p><strong>Skills for Success</strong></p><ul><li>At least GCE O/A Level or ITE in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering.</li><li>Training will be provided.</li><li>Have knowledge of hydraulic and diesel machineries.</li><li>Basic knowledge of welding and metal works.</li><li>A team worker and possess good communications skills</li><li>Enjoy hands-on manual and outdoor work/operations.</li><li>Able to climb height and lift heavy objects.</li></ul><p><strong>Your Career Growth Starts Here. Apply Now!</strong></p>",
